---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Daxxify | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Daxxify smooths wrinkles with peptide-powered technology, lasting up to 6–9 months for fewer treatments per year.", "canonical": "/services/daxxify", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---



<BaseLayout {...seo}>
<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{ --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8; }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="font-semibold leading-[1.05] md:text-6xl mt-2 text-[2.75rem] text-center tracking-tight">Daxxify</h1>
<div class="mx-auto mt-8 h-px w-48 md:w-64 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black to-transparent"></div>



      
      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">

      <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <p class="text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-900 measure">
          Daxxify (daxibotulinumtoxinA-lanm) is an advanced injectable treatment for dynamic wrinkles caused by repeated facial movements.
          It works by temporarily relaxing targeted muscles to soften lines such as frown lines and forehead creases. Unlike other neuromodulators,
          Daxxify uses a novel peptide stabilizer instead of human or animal-derived proteins, contributing to its extended duration of effect.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 measure">
          Clinical studies have shown results typically lasting about six months, with some patients maintaining smoother skin for up to nine months.
          This longer effect means fewer sessions per year compared to traditional wrinkle relaxers.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-attributes mt-6 flex flex-nowrap whitespace-nowrap items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2 md:gap-3 overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible pr-1" role="list"><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Peptide-powered</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>6+ months</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>FDA-approved</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Natural finish</li></ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 measure">“Long-lasting smoothness, fewer visits.”</p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-3">
        </div></section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PROCESS -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">1</div><p class="tl-title">Consultation</p><p class="muted mt-1">A personalized review of your facial concerns, goals, and medical history to confirm candidacy for Daxxify.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">2</div><p class="tl-title">Treatment</p><p class="muted mt-1">Precise injections with a fine needle target specific muscles. The session is quick and minimally uncomfortable.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">3</div><p class="tl-title">Follow‑Up</p><p class="muted mt-1">Results begin in 1–2 days, with full effect in about 2 weeks. Benefits last months, with maintenance typically twice a year.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE & POST -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div><p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Avoid alcohol and non‑prescribed blood thinners for 24 hours.</li>
              <li>Do not smoke the day prior; avoid harsh skincare treatments before your session.</li>
              <li>Arrive with a clean, makeup‑free face.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div><p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Stay upright for 4 hours; avoid rubbing treated areas.</li>
              <li>Skip strenuous activity, saunas, or hot tubs for 24 hours.</li>
              <li>Expect full results to appear in 1–2 weeks.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQS -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How is Daxxify different from Botox or Xeomin?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Daxxify uses a peptide stabilizer and lasts longer—often 6 months or more—compared to the 3–4 month duration of Botox or Xeomin.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">When will I see results?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Initial smoothing can be seen in 1–2 days, with full effects at 2 weeks.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How long do results last?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Most patients experience results for about 6 months, with some lasting up to 9 months.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Is Daxxify safe?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Yes, it is FDA‑approved and has a safety profile similar to other neuromodulators. Mild redness or bruising may occur temporarily.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How often will I need treatments?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Usually twice per year, since Daxxify lasts longer than other wrinkle relaxers.</p></details>
        </div>
      </section>

    </article>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
